296
00:32:43,760 --> 00:32:44,240
[SPEAKER_01] Znaš kako?

297
00:32:53,600 --> 00:32:57,280
[SPEAKER_01] Čovek koji zna za Boga, on se nema čega da se boji.

298
00:32:57,680 --> 00:32:58,000
