00:35:24,880 --> 00:35:24,880
[UNKNOWN] Uvijek je bilo.

314
00:35:26,000 --> 00:35:27,280
[SPEAKER_01] I onda su nagrabusili.

315
00:35:27,840 --> 00:35:29,600
